\begin_layout Standard
Ecuador is located in the north-west side of South-America (see Figure 1).
 The country has a diverse geography.
 It comprises a continental territory between the latitudes 01o 28’ N and
 05o 02’ S and longitudes 75o 11’ W and 81o 04’ W 
